{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_01CokxKdC58WGmW567PM67Jt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I have all the information I need. Here's the complete implementation:\n\n## Implementation\n\n### 1. New file: `config/monitoring/prometheus-rules.yaml`\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: monitoring.coreos.com/v1\nkind: PrometheusRule\nmetadata:\n  labels:\n    control-plane: controller-manager\n    app.kubernetes.io/name: prometheusrule\n    app.kubernetes.io/instance: multiarch-tuning-operator\n    app.kubernetes.io/component: monitoring\n    app.kubernetes.io/created-by: multiarch-tuning-operator\n    app.kubernetes.io/part-of: multiarch-tuning-operator\n    app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: kustomize\n  name: image-inspection-alerts\n  namespace: system\nspec:\n  groups:\n    - name: multiarch-tuning-operator.rules\n      rules:\n        - alert: MultiarchImageInspectionFailureRateCritical\n          expr: |\n            (\n              rate(mto_ppo_ctrl_failed_image_inspection_total[5m])\n              /\n              rate(mto_ppo_ctrl_processed_pods_total[5m])\n            ) > 0.05\n          for: 5m\n          labels:\n            severity: critical\n          annotations:\n            message: >-\n              Image inspection failure rate has exceeded 5% over the last 5 minutes.\n              Current failure rate is {{ $value | humanizePercentage }}.\n              This may indicate issues with image registry connectivity or\n              authentication affecting the multiarch tuning operator.\n```\n\n### 2. New file: `config/monitoring/kustomization.yaml`\n\n```yaml\nresources:\n- prometheus-rules.yaml\n```\n\n### 3. Modify: `config/default/kustomization.yaml`\n\nAdd `../monitoring` to the resources list:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: kustomize.config.k8s.io/v1beta1\nkind: Kustomization\nresources:\n- ../crd\n- ../rbac\n- ../manager\n- ../webhook\n- ../monitoring\n```\n\n### Explanation\n\n**Metric counters used:**\n- `mto_ppo_ctrl_failed_image_inspection_total` — defined in `internal/controller/podplacement/metrics/controller.go:66`, incremented in `internal/controller/podplacement/pod_model.go:502` when an image inspection fails.\n- `mto_ppo_ctrl_processed_pods_total` — defined in `internal/controller/podplacement/metrics/controller.go:60`, incremented in `internal/controller/podplacement/pod_reconciler.go:88` for each pod processed by the controller.\n\n**Alert expression:** `rate(failed) / rate(processed) > 0.05` computes the failure rate over a 5-minute window and fires when it exceeds 5%. The `for: 5m` clause ensures the condition must persist for 5 minutes before the alert fires, preventing transient spikes from paging.\n\n**No commands to run.** The YAML is declarative — it gets deployed with `kustomize build config/default | kubectl apply -f -` or via the operator's existing deployment pipeline."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":816,"cache_read_input_tokens":38675,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":816,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"35c526ac-3874-4025-a671-cd9acf755f45","uuid":"b583334a-c134-48fc-8a9e-0bdab1be7c8a","timestamp":"2026-07-20T14:54:24.514Z","request_id":"req_vrtx_011CdDW2DQFoNDs9u5CJP3Kt"}
