\n- ../monitoring\n```\n\n### Explanation\n\n**Metric counters used:**\n- `mto_ppo_ctrl_failed_image_inspection_total` \u2014 defined in `internal/controller/podplacement/metrics/controller.go:66`, incremented in `internal/controller/podplacement/pod_model.go:502` when an image inspection fails.\n- `mto_ppo_ctrl_processed_pods_total` \u2014 defined in `internal/controller/podplacement/metrics/controller.go:60`, incremented in `internal/controller/podplacement/pod_reconciler.go:88` for each pod processed by the controller.\n\n**Alert expression:** `rate(failed) / rate(processed) > 0.05` computes the failure rate over a 5-minute window and fires when it exceeds 5%. The `for: 5m` clause ensures the condition must persist for 5 minutes before the alert fires, preventing transient spikes from paging.\n\n**No commands to run.** The YAML is declarative \u2014 it gets deployed with `kustomize build config/default | kubectl apply -f -` or via the operator's existing deployment pipeline.", "stop_reason": "end_turn", "session_id": "35c526ac-3874-4025-a671-cd9acf755f45", "total_cost_usd": 0.263314, "usage": {"input_tokens": 8, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 16464, "cache_read_input_tokens": 203398, "output_tokens": 2347, "server_tool_use": {"web_search_requests": 0, "web_fetch_requests": 0}, "service_tier": "standard", "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 16464}, "inference_geo": "", "iterations": [], "speed": "standard"}, "modelUsage": {"claude-opus-4-6": {"inputTokens": 8, "outputTokens": 2347, "cacheReadInputTokens": 203398, "cacheCreationInputTokens": 16464, "webSearchRequests": 0, "costUSD": 0.263314, "contextWindow": 200000, "maxOutputTokens": 64000}}, "permission_denials": [], "terminal_reason": "completed", "fast_mode_state": "off", "uuid": "3e533c60-b18c-4bbb-a87a-04cd7fd1f28b", "timestamp": "2026-07-20T14:54:24.531Z"}